# LAMMPS task file for neb 
 
      dimension   2
     atom_style bond
     boundary   f f p
     bond_style harmonic
     atom_modify	map array sort 0 0.0

     variable  u uloop 20
     read_data  src/polygon/lammps_util/script/test_healty.lj708488
     timestep  0.1
     fix 1 all neb 1.0 parallel ideal

     thermo 100
     fix 2 all enforce2d
     dump 1 all atom 10 src/polygon/temp/dump.neb.$u
      min_style quickmin
     neb 1e-08 0.0 2000 2000 40 final src/polygon/lammps_util/script/prion_neb_pos.lj708488
